<ab facs="#facs_309_r2l17">die ~ kürfürſten <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> cʒu franckfurt <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> gnedigen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> den künig </ab>
